    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>tomatoes</strong> roughly </p><p>Add the<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> to the pan and cook over a medium heat for 4 min or until thickened to a curry-like consistency</p><p>Once thickened, add the<strong> spinach</strong> and cook for a further 5-6 min or until it's wilted</p>",
